                     DEFINICON SYSTEMS, INC.



                    DSI-32 COPROCESSOR BOARD
                   & MS/PC DOS SYSTEM SOFTWARE




        




     ASSEMBLER / LINKER

     REFERENCE MANUAL











The Definicon Systems Assembler was developed by Computer Systems 
Design,  North Perth Australia, for the DSI-32 coprocessor board.  
All  references  to Definicon Systems Assembler for the  National 
Semiconductor  32032  are references to the CSD  version  of  the 
assembler.
